•
I react to the JONAS BROTHERS new single and I give you guys 10 other dope ass song recommendations. The occasional dancing & singing along to them might be included 🤷🏻‍♀️😏
Ik. Ik. Ik. It’s been like 9 months since I last made a YouTube video, 😩 but I’m back & I’m better & I’m so excited for you guys to see what I’ve got planned for this year. 😍😝🥳

blog.title: Your Daily Queer
blog.description:
"We’re here! We’re queer! We’re filled with existential fear"

YDQ is a blog that posts daily content of those famous who are LGBTQ+ and since Dec 2018 has posted over 1000 queers and has 3.2k followers.

This blog will also post historical LGBTQ+ people as it will surprise you who was Queer in the past.

Send an ask or submit if you want someone to appear here. There are 300 queers in queue at any one time. Love to read tags of reblogged posts.

Do you guys know what I like the most about the commentary crew? That they actually interact with their viewers! Like, I just watched Hooverr’s instagram live and he read like at least half of my comments and responded to them?? And Ani, Kappa, Aksel, Quackity AND Henry all commented on the same video I made where they were mentioned???

Like, most youtubers don’t do this but these people do and it honestly makes me so happy!
